Virial-Based Intraatomic and Interatomic Energy Contributions:
-------------------------------------------------------------
  E_Intra(A) = T(A) + Ven(A,A) + Vee(A,A)
             = Intraatomic Contribution to E(A)
  E_Inter(A) = Ven(A,A') + Vee(A,A')/2 + Vnn(A)
             = Interatomic Contribution to E(A) = E(A) - E_Intra(A)
  Ee_Intra(A) = T(A) + Ven(A,A) + Vee(A,A)
              = Intraatomic Contribution to Ee(A)
  Ee_Inter(A) = Ven(A,A') + Vee(A,A')/2 + Vnn(A) - W(A)
              = Interatomic Contribution to Ee(A) = Ee(A) - Ee_Intra(A)
See "2EDM Note" and "DFT Note".
